      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CANYA REDLINE (2) was strongly fancied latest and proved too good with a 1.5 lengths win at this track in a handy 34.82. Fair draw can see a good run and goes well at this distance. Winner at his latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Makes plenty of appeal if runs up to latest. WEST ON MENACE (8) settled midfield in the run and boxed on to finish there when 4th (27.78) at Mandurah. Yet to win at the journey but has run some good races. Key runner who gets her chance to atone. IMPRESS KUTA (1) has a moderate overall strike-rate. Hit the board with a minor placing last time when third (35.08) at this track. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings four times from seven starts. Expected to be in the finish again. SWEET MICHELLE (7) cannot be dismissed although new to this distance.",
